text:
Farcaster now supports 3x longer casts!

Long casts can have up to 1024 simple characters. The first few lines will show up in the feed and you can tap Show More to read the rest.   

Warpcast supports creating long casts on mobile and on web. You may need to restart your mobile app to get the latest changes.  

A big thanks to @vrypan @df @sanjay @gt @piril @sds and many others who contributed to getting this over the finish line!
Should help non-Latin character languages since the limit will go from 320 bytes to 1024 bytes.
